"msg":"真係up足兩星期？ 咁點沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:26:22.000Z","msg":"個時靠用毛巾濕水抹唔係生蛇個啲位<br />\n<br />\n生蛇個啲位係無抹過"},{"pid":"7bcb3ee2fa8c6e4251d3bc2836739324ed218b4c","tid":797720,"uid":38318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:52:44.000Z","msg":"生緊 睇西醫話食藥一個星期好 唔食就四個星期自己會好 同埋唔使搽野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2778e958f4eef551609f25f519a2d1a83269fa","tid":797720,"uid":35560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:27:07.000Z","msg":"前排成日深夜睇波生蛇<br />\n明明日日都訓夠8個鐘都生<br />\n一開始完全唔痛唔痕 以為生濕疹<br />\n去到第四日朝早越生越多後尾send 相問人 個個都話我生蛇 即刻睇醫生<br />\n食左五日藥好返晒<br />\n但d印仲係度<br />\n比較好彩既係食緊第三日藥先有小小痛 好似有傷口果隻痛<br />\n<br />\n不過上網睇話好小人會生兩次蛇，其實係唔係？"},{"pid":"fca53659affff20b49ea2a312df316d9e11c72c8","tid":797720,"uid":201071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"我都係上個月生完<br />\n依家條頸仲係好多紅色1點點"},{"pid":"f4809cb213de8feb07cba502989fb05d43f1b4d7","tid":797720,"uid":25641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a4d12f5624a57d3491602e2ea37e327d7847203","tid":797720,"uid":154470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bcb3ee2fa8c6e4251d3bc2836739324ed218b4c","tid":797720,"uid":38318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:52:44.000Z","msg":"生緊 睇西醫話食藥一個星期好 唔食就四個星期自己會好 同埋唔使搽野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T15:59:01.000Z","msg":"我睇個陣都有藥膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3aa88d9c1c26865e62429541442f9c602a4a125","tid":797720,"uid":154470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fca53659affff20b49ea2a312df316d9e11c72c8","tid":797720,"uid":201071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply